{"tid":2415526,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【經典香港歌】 會過去的 (許志安+車婉婉)","createTime":"2021-02-20T10:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T11:02:20.000Z","uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c56bd83ff2864e6887bea803b6d428c7002fe69a","tid":2415526,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"會過去的 (許志安+車婉婉)  <br />\n派台年份 : 2000年<br />\n<br />\n原來已經21年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xaTBCCMHZ-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxaTBCCMHZ-E&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkvLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=479a791f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xaTBCCMHZ-E</a><br />\n<br />\n及後在2000年，屬正東唱片的許志安計劃與車婉婉製作一首合唱歌，以推動車的歌唱事業[註 1]。於是她主動聯絡陳輝陽為《會過去的》作曲[註 1]；該曲未幾成為車婉婉的首本名曲[10]，推出初期沒有登上很多歌曲排名榜[註 1]，後受電台唱片騎師熱播，令歌曲變得街知巷聞。不但成為卡拉OK場地受歡迎的合唱歌曲[7]，她更憑此曲首次獲得多個樂壇獎項，如2001年叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮「專業推介．叱咤十大」。"},{"pid":"fbd1747c19e457a9c1e12b6209c9291082587e01","tid":2415526,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"經典石頭歌"},{"pid":"7ed35393b83b78a0ae3c65508c11759fe1ab21a3","tid":2415526,"uid":5253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"石頭都會過去　都會散去 <br />\n為何連青山都太累"},{"pid":"3d7c5346487978f19f9821f6976abef486ff4af9","tid":2415526,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}